<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Menu Futuro | Chiapas Treats in the PNW</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --cream: #fff6df;
      --masa: #ffe7a3;
      --mango: #ffb703;
      --papaya: #fb8500;
      --chile: #d62828;
      --rosa: #ff5ca8;
      --verde: #2a9d8f;
      --azul: #0077b6;
      --cacao: #4b2e1f;
      --white: #ffffff;
    }* {
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: "Trebuchet MS", Arial, sans-serif;
  color: var(--cacao);
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(255, 92, 168, 0.22), transparent 30%),
    radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(42, 157, 143, 0.25), transparent 35%),
    linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cream), #fffaf0 55%, #ffe9b8);
  min-height: 100vh;
}

.papel {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  pointer-events: none;
  opacity: 0.22;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(45deg, var(--rosa) 25%, transparent 25%),
    linear-gradient(-45deg, var(--verde) 25%, transparent 25%),
    linear-gradient(45deg, transparent 75%, var(--azul) 75%),
    linear-gradient(-45deg, transparent 75%, var(--mango) 75%);
  background-size: 72px 72px;
  background-position: 0 0, 0 36px, 36px -36px, -36px 0px;
  mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, black 0%, transparent 48%);
}

header {
  position: relative;
  padding: 28px 20px 12px;
  text-align: center;
}

.badge {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 8px 16px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  color: var(--white);
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--verde), var(--azul));
  font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.14);
}

h1 {
  margin: 18px auto 8px;
  max-width: 920px;
  font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 10vw, 8rem);
  line-height: 0.9;
  color: var(--chile);
  text-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--masa), 8px 8px 0 rgba(251, 133, 0, 0.25);
  letter-spacing: -0.06em;
}

.subtitle {
  margin: 0 auto;
  max-width: 760px;
  font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 3vw, 2rem);
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--cacao);
}

.hero {
  position: relative;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr minmax(280px, 520px) 1fr;
  gap: 22px;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 28px 20px 50px;
}

.side-card {
  min-height: 280px;
  border-radius: 36px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
  border: 3px dashed rgba(214, 40, 40, 0.35);
  box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
  padding: 24px;
  text-align: center;
}

.icon {
  font-size: clamp(4rem, 10vw, 8rem);
  filter: drop-shadow(0 8px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.13));
}

.side-card p {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  margin: 12px 0 0;
}

.menu-card {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  padding: 34px 28px;
  border-radius: 44px;
  background: var(--white);
  border: 6px solid var(--chile);
  box-shadow:
    0 24px 60px rgba(75,46,31,0.25),
    inset 0 0 0 8px var(--masa);
  text-align: center;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.menu-card::before,
.menu-card::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  width: 150px;
  height: 150px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  opacity: 0.16;
  z-index: -1;
}

.menu-card::before {
  background: var(--rosa);
  left: -40px;
  top: -40px;
}

.menu-card::after {
  background: var(--verde);
  right: -45px;
  bottom: -45px;
}

.menu-title {
  margin: 0 0 8px;
  font-size: 1rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  color: var(--azul);
  font-weight: 900;
}

h2 {
  margin: 0 0 26px;
  font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4.6rem);
  color: var(--papaya);
  text-shadow: 3px 3px 0 var(--masa);
}

.menu-list {
  display: grid;
  gap: 16px;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  list-style: none;
}

.menu-list li {
  padding: 18px 20px;
  border-radius: 24px;
  font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
  font-weight: 900;
  color: var(--white);
  box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.14);
  transform: rotate(-1deg);
}

.menu-list li:nth-child(1) { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--rosa), var(--chile)); }
.menu-list li:nth-child(2) { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--verde), var(--azul)); transform: rotate(1deg); }
.menu-list li:nth-child(3) { background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--mango), var(--papaya)); }

.tagline-section {
  margin: -8px auto 42px;
  max-width: 980px;
  padding: 0 20px;
  text-align: center;
}

.tagline {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 24px 28px;
  border-radius: 32px;
  background: var(--cacao);
  color: var(--cream);
  font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 3vw, 2.25rem);
  font-weight: 900;
  line-height: 1.2;
  box-shadow: 0 16px 34px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
}

.locations {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 10px;
  margin-top: 18px;
}

.locations span {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.76);
  border: 2px solid rgba(75,46,31,0.18);
  border-radius: 999px;
  padding: 10px 16px;
  font-weight: 800;
}

footer {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 22px 20px 34px;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: rgba(75,46,31,0.75);
}

@media (max-width: 850px) {
  .hero {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .side-card {
    min-height: 160px;
  }
}

  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="papel"></div>  <header>
    <div class="badge">Mexican Treats • Coming Soon</div>
    <h1>Menu Futuro</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Sweet street treats made for parks, festivals, sunny days, and happy families.</p>
  </header>  <main>
    <section class="hero" aria-label="Featured menu">
      <div class="side-card">
        <div>
          <div class="icon">🍓</div>
          <p>Fresh, creamy, colorful, and joyful.</p>
        </div>
      </div><div class="menu-card">
    <p class="menu-title">Featured Menu</p>
    <h2>Antojitos Dulces</h2>
    <ul class="menu-list">
      <li>Fresas con Crema</li>
      <li>Gomitas</li>
      <li>Mini Pancakes</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="side-card">
    <div>
      <div class="icon">🥞</div>
      <p>Perfect for festivals, parks, and community events.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="tagline-section">
  <div class="tagline">
    We operate in parks and festivals, bringing the flavor of Chiapas to the PNW.
  </div>
  <div class="locations" aria-label="Service areas">
    <span>Everett</span>
    <span>Snohomish</span>
    <span>Monroe</span>
    <span>Marysville</span>
    <span>Lake Stevens</span>
    <span>Snohomish County</span>
  </div>
</section>

  </main>  <footer>
    Follow the sweetness. More treats coming soon.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>